<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Reset Password - Byte Beyond Persona</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f0f2f1;
      font-family: &quot;Montserrat&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    "
  >
    <table
      width="100%"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="padding: 40px 20px"
    >
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table
            width="750"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            style="
              background-color: #ffffff;
              border-radius: 0px;
              overflow: hidden;
              box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            "
          >
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  background-color: #000000;
                  padding: 50px 40px;
                  text-align: center;
                "
              >
                <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
                  <img
                    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhdpnfvfn/image/upload/v1769745581/byte-beyond-persona-logo_novsd8.svg"
                    alt="Byte Beyond Persona Logo"
                    class="logo"
                    style="width: 400px; height: auto; display: inline-block"
                  />
                </div>
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 20px 0 0;
                    font-size: 13px;
                    color: #ffffff;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 4px;
                    opacity: 0.8;
                    font-weight: 300;
                  "
                >
                  Secure Account Recovery
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 60px 50px">
                <h2
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 24px;
                    font-size: 24px;
                    font-weight: 400;
                    color: #1a1a1a;
                    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                  "
                >
                  Hi
                  <strong>{{firstName}}</strong>,
                </h2>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 18px;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    color: #444444;
                    font-weight: 400;
                  "
                >
                  Kami menerima permintaan untuk mengatur ulang kata sandi akun
                  Anda.
                </p>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 32px;
                    font-size: 16px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                    color: #444444;
                  "
                >
                  Klik tombol di bawah ini untuk melanjutkan proses reset
                  password. Tautan ini hanya berlaku selama
                  <strong>15 menit</strong>.
                </p>

                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0 0 40px;
                    font-size: 14px;
                    line-height: 1.6;
                    color: #888888;
                    border-left: 2px solid #00a86b;
                    padding-left: 20px;
                  "
                >
                  <em>If you did not request this password reset, please ignore
                    this email. Your account will remain secure.</em>
                </p>

                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                  <tr>
                    <td align="center">
                      <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                        <tr>
                          <td
                            style="
                              background-color: #00a86b;
                              border-radius: 0px;
                            "
                          >
                            <a
                              href="{{resetPasswordLink}}"
                              style="
                                display: inline-block;
                                padding: 20px 50px;
                                font-size: 14px;
                                font-weight: 700;
                                color: #ffffff;
                                text-decoration: none;
                                text-transform: uppercase;
                                letter-spacing: 2px;
                              "
                            >
                              Reset Password
                            </a>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <div
                  style="
                    margin: 50px auto 0;
                    width: 40px;
                    height: 1px;
                    background-color: #ffcc00;
                  "
                ></div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 0 50px 50px; text-align: center">
                <p
                  style="
                    margin: 0;
                    font-size: 11px;
                    color: #bbbbbb;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 1px;
                    line-height: 1.8;
                  "
                >
                  Jika Anda tidak meminta reset password, abaikan email ini.<br
                  />
                  <span style="font-size: 10px">If you didn't request a password
                    reset, please ignore this message.</span>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td height="5" style="background-color: #ffcc00"></td>
            </tr>
          </table>

          <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
              <td
                style="
                  padding: 30px;
                  text-align: center;
                  color: #aaaaaa;
                  font-size: 11px;
                  letter-spacing: 1px;
                "
              >
                &copy; 2024 PT BYTE BEYOND PERSONA. ESTABLISHED FOR EXCELLENCE.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>